        "subject": "LU-1280 ldiskfs: remove LASSERTF from ext3_ext_new_extent_cb()",
        "message": "LU-1280 ldiskfs: remove LASSERTF from ext3_ext_new_extent_cb()\n\nThe LASSERTF() in ext3_ext_new_extent_cb() was injected for\ndebugging purpose to make sure the race really happened but\nwas forgotten to be removed from the original patch in\nhttp://review.whamcloud.com/1618 .\n\nThe EXT_ASSERT() in ext3_ext_new_extent_cb() is also invalid\nsince new locking is introduced in ext4_ext_walk_space().\n\nSigned-off-by: Yu Jian <yujian@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I9974e3849d8e3c2f1423769645dd2a914f35d9eb\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/b2_2"
    }
